HEADWORD: Summons
<hw>Sum"mons</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To summon.</def> <mark>[R. or
Colloq.]</mark> <rj><au>Swift.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Summum bonum</ent>⟦br⟧
